# {{.Name}} Design System

This document outlines the design system for {{.Name}} mobile applications, ensuring consistency across Android and iOS platforms.

## Brand Identity

### Logo
- Primary logo: Use the full logo with text
- Icon only: Use for small spaces (app icons, favicons)
- Minimum size: 24px for icon, 120px for full logo
- Clear space: Minimum 1x logo height on all sides

### Typography

#### Primary Font: Inter
- **Headings**: Inter Bold (700)
- **Body Text**: Inter Regular (400)
- **Captions**: Inter Light (300)

#### Secondary Font: Roboto (Android fallback)
- **Headings**: Roboto Bold (700)
- **Body Text**: Roboto Regular (400)
- **Captions**: Roboto Light (300)

#### Font Scales
- **Display**: 32sp/32pt
- **Headline**: 24sp/24pt
- **Title**: 20sp/20pt
- **Body Large**: 16sp/16pt
- **Body Medium**: 14sp/14pt
- **Body Small**: 12sp/12pt
- **Caption**: 10sp/10pt

